                        "text": "vine +11 [<a aonid=\"322\" game-obj=\"Rules\"><u>+7/+3</u></a>] (<a aonid=\"170\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>agile</u></a>, <a aonid=\"192\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>reach 10 feet</u></a>), <b>Damage</b> 1d8+4 slashing plus weeping wounds",
