        {
            "name": "Deadly Flora",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Locations",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "These deadly organisms can be found in any hot or temperate environment, but like most plants, they need light and moisture to thrive.",
                    "source": {
                        "type": "source",
                        "name": "The Fall of Plaguestone",
                        "link": {
